Sally   Grimes  President of North American Retail, Tyson Foods, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.46--
Background

		Ms. Sally Grimes has been the President of North American Retail at Tyson Foods, Inc. since February 14, 2017 and served as its Chief Global Growth Officer and President of International from September 2014 to February 14, 2017. Ms. Grimes served as Executive Officer of Insights, Innovation, R&D, Retail Sales and Global Brand Strategy at Tyson Foods, Inc. She served as President and Global Growth Officer at Tyson Foods, Inc., since September 2014. Ms. Grimes served as ... Chief Innovation Officer at The Hillshire Brands Company since July 2012 and served as its President of Gourmet Food Group since July 2012. Ms. Grimes served as a Senior Vice President at The Hillshire Brands Company since July 2012. Prior to Hillshire Brands, Ms. Grimes served as Global Vice President of Marketing, for the writing and creative expression business unit at Newell Rubbermaid, Inc. (global marketer of consumer and commercial products) from July 2007 to June 2012 and worked at Kraft Foods, Inc. (branded food products) in a variety of brand management positions from 1997 to 2007.Read Full Background




